<item>
            <title>[LU-19804] &quot;mv&quot; can skip the project quota enforcement</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19804</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when moving a file into a directory with project inheritance flag, it can ignore the quota&lt;br/&gt;
enforcement and cause the project quota to be over limit.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;# lfs quota -p 1000 -h /mnt/lustre
Disk quotas for prj prjid1000 (pid 1000):
     Filesystem    used  bquota  blimit  bgrace   files  iquota  ilimit  igrace 
    /mnt/lustre    297M      0k    300M       -       5       0       0       - 
# lfs project /mnt/lustre/
 1000 P /mnt/lustre//tdir
# lfs project /mnt/lustre/tdir
 1000 - /mnt/lustre/tdir/tfile3
 1000 - /mnt/lustre/tdir/tfile2
 1000 - /mnt/lustre/tdir/tfile4
 1000 - /mnt/lustre/tdir/tfile1

# dd if=/dev/zero of=/mnt/lustre/tfile bs=1M count=100
100+0 records in
100+0 records out
104857600 bytes (105 MB, 100 MiB) copied, 0.333245 s, 315 MB/s

# mv /mnt/lustre/tfile /mnt/lustre/tdir/
# lfs project /mnt/lustre/tdir/
 1000 - /mnt/lustre/tdir//tfile3
 1000 - /mnt/lustre/tdir//tfile2
 1000 - /mnt/lustre/tdir//tfile
 1000 - /mnt/lustre/tdir//tfile4
 1000 - /mnt/lustre/tdir//tfile1
# lfs quota -p 1000 -h /mnt/lustre
Disk quotas for prj prjid1000 (pid 1000):
     Filesystem    used  bquota  blimit  bgrace   files  iquota  ilimit  igrace 
    /mnt/lustre   394M*      0k    300M       -      6*       0       0       - 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
